```
npm install discord.js discord.js-commando
```
Once you have installed Discord.js and the Discord.js CLI, you can create a new bot by running the following command in your terminal:
```
discord.js-commando init botname
```
This will create a new bot with the specified name. You can then add the following code to the `bot.js` file to create a bot with one command, ban:
